Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
First and foremost dont go to a college just because all of your friends are going there, your taking loans that youll have to pay off once you finish and you want to make sure that your able to get the best educatioj and job you can.  Second find a school that has programs that your interested in.  if you like programming look for schools that have up to date computer labs.  Finally dont feel bad if you dont get accepted by your first choice, there are tons of great schools that have programs like that one.  Also try to stay in state because its a lot cheaper.